\c 19
\s UPawuli eEfesu
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi, uApolosi\x + 18.24.\x* eseseKorinte\x + 18.1. 18.27.\x*, uPawuli wafika eEfesu\x + 19.17,26,28,34,35. 18.19.\x* esedabule indawo eziphakemeyo; wasefica abafundi abathile
\v 2 wathi kubo: Lamemukela yini uMoya oNgcwele mhla likholwayo? Basebesithi kuye: Kodwa kasizanga sizwe ngitsho ukuthi kukhona uMoya oNgcwele\x + Joha. 7.39. 1 Sam. 3.7. Seb. 8.16.\x*.
\v 3 Wasesithi kubo: Pho labhabhathizelwa kukuphi? Basebesithi: Kubhabhathizo lukaJohane\x + 18.25.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa uPawuli wathi: UJohane isibili wabhabhathiza ubhabhathizo lokuphenduka\x + Mat. 3.11. Seb. 13.24,25.\x*, etshela abantu ukuze bakholwe kulowo oweza emva kwakhe, okuyikuthi, kuKristu Jesu\x + Joha. 1.7.\x*.
\v 5 Lalabo abezwayo babhabhathizwa ebizweni leNkosi uJesu\x + 8.16. 10.48. Mat. 28.19.\x*.
\v 6 Wathi uPawuli esebeke izandla phezu kwabo\x + 8.17. Heb. 6.2. Seb. 6.6.\x*, uMoya oyiNgcwele weza phezu kwabo; basebekhuluma ngendimi\x + 10.46. 2.4.\x*, baprofetha\x + 21.9. 1 Kor. 11.4,5. 13.9. 14.1,3-5. Seb. 11.27.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo wonke amadoda ayengaba litshumi lambili.
\p
\v 8 Wasengena esinagogeni\x + 13.14.\x* wakhuluma ngesibindi, inyanga ezintathu\x + 4.29.\x* etshumayela\x + 17.17.\x* eqinisekisa izinto ngombuso kaNkulunkulu\x + 28.23. 1.3.\x*.
\v 9 Kodwa kwathi abanye besiba lukhuni bengakholwa, bekhuluma kubi nga\add leyo\add*ndlela phambi kwabantu\x + 19.23. 9.2. 2 Pet. 2.2.\x*, wasuka kubo\x + 19.8. 28.28.\x* wehlukanisa abafundi\x + 19.30. 11.26.\x*, insuku ngensuku etshumayela esikolo sothile uTiranu\x + 17.17.\x*.
\v 10 Lalokhu kwenzeka okweminyaka emibili\x + 19.8. 20.31.\x*, baze balizwa ilizwi leNkosi uJesu bonke abakhileyo eAsiya\x + 19.22,26,27. 2.9.\x*, amaJuda kanye lamaGriki.
\v 11 UNkulunkulu wasesenza\x + 5.12.\x* imisebenzi yamandla engejwayelekanga ngezandla zikaPawuli\x + 28.2.\x*,
\v 12 kwaze kwathi lakwabagulayo kwasiwa izifinyo kumbe amafasikoti\x + Luka 19.20.\x* okuvela emzimbeni wakhe\x + Mat. 14.36.\x*, lezifo zasuka kubo, labomoya ababi baphuma kubo\x + Mark. 16.17.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Kwathi abanye kumihambuma yamaJuda, izanuse\x + Mat. 12.27. Luka 11.19.\x*, bazama ukubiza ibizo leNkosi uJesu kulabo ababelabomoya ababi, besithi: Siyalifungisa ngoJesu amtshumayelayo uPawuli\x + Mark. 9.38. Luka 9.49. Mat. 7.22.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo kwakukhona amadodana ayisikhombisa athile kaSikeva umJuda umpristi omkhulu akwenzayo lokho\x + 5.24. 9.14,21.\x*.
\v 15 Kodwa umoya omubi waphendula wathi: UJesu ngiyamazi, loPawuli ngiyazi ngaye; kodwa lina lingobani?
\v 16 Lowomuntu okwakukuye umoya omubi waseseqela phezu kwabo, njalo wabehlula, wabanqoba, baze babaleka kuleyondlu benqunu belimele.
\v 17 Lokhu kwasekusaziwa yibo bonke abakhileyo eEfesu\x + 19.1,26.\x* amaJuda kanye lamaGriki; lokwesaba kwasekubehlela bonke\x + 2.43.\x*; njalo lakhuliswa ibizo leNkosi uJesu.
\v 18 Labanengi balabo abakholwayo beza, bevuma, bememezela izenzo zabo\x + Mat. 3.6.\x*.
\v 19 Labanengi balabo ababesenza amasalamusi baletha ingwalo ndawonye bazitshisa phambi kwabo bonke; basebebala intengo yazo, bathola izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amahlanu zesiliva\x + Luka 15.8.\x*.
\v 20 Ngokunjalo ilizwi leNkosi lakhula ngamandla lanqoba\x + 6.7. 12.24.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Kwathi lezizinto seziphelile, uPawuli wazimisela emoyeni\x + 5.4.\x*, esedabule\x + 1 Kor. 16.5. 2 Kor. 1.16.\x* eMakedoniya\x + 16.12.\x* leAkaya\x + Roma 15.26; 18.12. 1 Thes. 1.7,8.\x*, ukuya eJerusalema\x + 20.22.\x*, esithi: Emva kokuba kwami lapho, ngimele ukubona iRoma layo\x + Roma 15.24-28. Seb. 23.11.\x*.
\v 22 Esethume eMakedoniya\x + 16.12.\x* ababili balabo ababemsiza\x + 13.5. 19.29.\x*, uTimothi\x + 16.1.\x* loErastu\x + Roma 16.23. 2 Tim. 4.20.\x*, yena wahlala eAsiya okwesikhathi\x + 2.9.\x*.
\s Isiphithiphithi sikaDemetriyu
\p
\v 23 Kodwa ngalesosikhathi kwasuka isiphithiphithi esingesincinyane\x + 2 Kor. 1.8.\x* mayelana la\add leyo\add*ndlela\x + 19.9.\x*.
\v 24 Ngoba umuntu othile onguDemetriyu ngebizo, umkhandi wesiliva, owenza amathempel\add ana\add* esiliva kaDiyana, waletha kuzingcwethi inzuzo engencinyane\x + 16.16,19.\x*;
\v 25 owabaqoqayo bona, lezisebenzi zezinto ezifananayo, wathi: Madoda, liyazi ukuthi inotho yethu ivela kulumsebenzi.
\v 26 Njalo liyabona liyezwa ukuthi kungeyisikho eEfesu\x + 19.1,26.\x* kuphela, kodwa phose kulo lonke iAsiya\x + 2.9.\x*, uPawuli lo uncengile njalo uphambule ixuku elikhulu, esithi kayisibo onkulunkulu abenziwe ngezandla\x + Hlab. 115.4.\x*.
\v 27 Njalo kayisikho lokhu kuphela ukuthi sisengozini yokuthi lolugatsha lomsebenzi lufike ekutheni lungahlonitshwa, kodwa lethempeli likankulunkulukazi omkhulu uDiyana lizathiwa liyinto engesilutho, njalo lobukhulukazi bakhe buzakwehliswa, elimkhonzayo yonke iAsiya\x + Luka 15.8.\x* lomhlaba wonke\x + Mat. 24.14.\x*.
\v 28 Kwathi be\add ku\add*zwa bagcwala intukuthelo, bamemeza besithi: Mkhulu uDiyana wamaEfesu!
\v 29 Njalo umuzi wonke wagcwala isiphithiphithi\x + 6.7. 12.24.\x*; basebetheleka kanyekanye endaweni yokudlalela, bahudula\x + 6.12.\x* uGayusi\x + 20.4. Roma 16.23. 1 Kor. 1.14.\x* loAristako\x + 20.4. 27.2. Kol. 4.10. Filim. 1.24.\x* amaMakedoniya, abaphelekezeli bakaPawuli\x + 2 Kor. 8.19.\x*.
\v 30 Kwathi uPawuli efuna ukungena exukwini, abafundi kabamvumelanga\x + 19.9.\x*.
\v 31 Njalo labanye bababusi beAsiya\x + 2.9.\x*, ababengabangane bakhe, bathuma kuye, be\add m\add*ncenga ukuthi angazinikeli endaweni yokudlalela.
\v 32 Ngakho abanye bamemeza okunye labanye okunye; ngoba umhlangano wawusanganisekile\x + 21.31. 19.29. 21.27.\x*, njalo inengi labo lalingazi ukuthi libuthene lapho ngenxa yani.
\v 33 Basebemusa phambili uAleksandro esuka exukwini\x + Mat. 14.8.\x*, ngoba amaJuda amqhubela phambili. UAleksandro\x + Mark. 15.21. 1 Tim. 1.20. 2 Tim. 4.14.\x* waseqhweba ngesandla\x + 12.17.\x*, efuna ukuzivikela ebantwini\x + 24.10. 25.8. 26.1,2,24. 25.16.\x*.
\v 34 Kodwa bathi sebekwazi ukuthi ungumJuda, kwaba lelizwi elilodwa livela kubo bonke okungaba ngamahola amabili limemeza \add lisithi\add*: Mkhulu uDiyana wamaEfesu!
\p
\v 35 Njalo kwathi umabhalane eselithulisile ixuku\x + 19.36.\x* wathi: Madoda eEfesu, kanti kukhona yini umuntu ongaziyo ukuthi umuzi weEfesu ungumlondolozi wethempeli likankulunkulukazi omkhulu uDiyana lowento eyawa ivela kuZewusi?
\v 36 Ngakho njengoba lezizinto zingephikwe, kufanele lithule\x + 19.36.\x*, lingenzi lutho ngamawala\x + 2 Tim. 3.4.\x*.
\v 37 Ngoba lilethe lamadoda, angeyisibo abaphangi bamathempeli langahlambazi unkulunkulukazi wenu.
\v 38 Ngakho uba uDemetriyu lezingcwethi kanye laye belodaba ngomuntu, amalanga okuthonisa amacala ayagcinwa, bakhona lababusi\x + 13.7.\x*; kabamangalelane\x + 19.40. 23.28,29. 26.2,7. Roma 8.33.\x*.
\v 39 Kodwa uba lidinga ulutho ngezinye izinto, kuzalungiswa emhlanganweni osemthethweni\f + \fk osemthethweni: \fl kumbe, \fq ojwayelekileyo.\f*.
\v 40 Ngoba futhi sisengozini yokumangalelwa ngomvukela ngenxa yalamuhla\x + 19.40. 23.28,29. 26.2,7. Roma 8.33.\x*, kungelambangela esingalandisa ngayo ngalesisiphithiphithi.
\v 41 Njalo esetshilo lokho, wawuchitha umhlangano.